<tr id="L151"><td><a href="#L151">151</a></td><td>O'BRIEN:  And what good will that do? You have no idea where he is. We don't know what we're up against, how strong he is, if he can be hurt by phaser fire.</td></tr>

<tr id="L152"><td><a href="#L152">152</a></td><td>DAX:  Don't worry Chief. I wasn't asking for any of your help. If he's here, I'll find him. Even if I have to do it all by myself.</td></tr>

